Questions submitted through e-mail will be reviewed by a
peer academic advisor or undergraduate counselor.

Due to the volume of e-mails received,
expect to wait a minimum of 2-3 business days for a response.If your question is complex or time sensitive, we
recommend that you come to walk-in hours or schedule an appointment.



